      Not through motivation. Through daily practice.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-subtitle mb-5 mx-auto text-secondary-color">
      Helping students, parents, and professionals practice life skills that transform daily behavior, strengthen families, build civic sense, and improve professional performance.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-ctas d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-content-center mb-5">
      <a href="#life-skills" class="btn-primary-lg shadow-glow-primary hover-scale text-decoration-none">BeYa Trainings</a>
      <a href="#medibuk" class="btn-secondary-lg hover-scale text-decoration-none">BeYa MediBuk</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Founder Quote -->
    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-4">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8">
        <div class="quote-card p-4 rounded-4 text-start shadow-glow-accent floating-slow">
          <i class="bi bi-quote display-4 text-accent opacity-50 floating-quote-icon"></i>
          <p class="fs-5 text-primary-color fst-italic mb-4 position-relative z-1 text-lh-17">
            "Living with paralysis, my mother taught me through how she lived—with patience, discipline, and dignity. BeYa is built from those lessons, and exists to make them possible for millions."
          </p>
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
             <div class="founder-hero-thumb flex-shrink-0">
               <%= image_tag "founder_photo.jpg", alt: "Sabith Ali", style: "position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;", onerror: "this.style.display='none'" rescue "" %>
               SA
             </div>
             <div>
               <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold text-primary-color">Sabith Ali</h6>
               <small class="text-secondary-color">Founder & System Architect, BeYa</small>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Metrics -->
    <div class="hero-metrics d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap gap-3 gap-md-4 mt-5 pt-3">
      <div class="metric-pill px-4 py-2 rounded-pill"><span class="fw-bold gradient-text-1">3,000+</span> <span class="text-secondary-color">Families Enrolled</span></div>
      <div class="metric-pill px-4 py-2 rounded-pill"><span class="fw-bold gradient-text-2">1M+</span> <span class="text-secondary-color">Patients via MediBuk</span></div>
      <div class="metric-pill px-4 py-2 rounded-pill"><span class="fw-bold gradient-text-3">13</span> <span class="text-secondary-color">Years of Practice</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 2. INTRO BAND -->
<section class="intro-band py-5 position-relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="intro-bg-glow"></div>
  <div class="container reveal text-center py-4 position-relative z-1">
    <h2 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-4 display-6 px-md-5 mx-md-5 intro-quote-title">
      “The most powerful change agent is already inside the system — waiting to be trained and trusted.”
    </h2>
    <a href="#about" class="btn-primary-lg shadow-glow-primary hover-scale text-decoration-none mt-2 d-inline-block">Discover BeYa</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 3. ABOUT SECTION -->
<section id="about" class="py-5 section-darker">
  <div class="container py-5 reveal">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-5 mb-5 mb-lg-0 pe-lg-5">
        <h6 class="text-uppercase text-secondary-color fw-bold mb-3 text-tracking-2">About Us</h6>
        <h2 class="fw-bold section-title mb-4">Not Inspiration.<br/><span class="gradient-text-1">Transformation.</span></h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-color fs-5 text-lh-17">
          BeYa is built on a simple conviction: lasting change does not come from external inspiration. It comes from within when people practice better habits every day. Across families, schools, workplaces, and hospitals, BeYa enables individuals to grow through structured daily practice.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary-color fs-5 text-lh-17">
          We do not insert external solutions into broken systems. We train and trust the people already inside them and enable them to create change from within.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-7">
        <div class="row g-4">
          <!-- Pillar 1 -->
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="feature-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4">
              <div class="feature-icon-box box-blue mb-3"><i class="bi bi-calendar-check-fill"></i></div>
              <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-2">Daily Practice</h5>
              <p class="text-secondary-color fs-sm m-0">Change happens through small, repeated actions — not one-time sessions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Pillar 2 -->
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="feature-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4">
              <div class="feature-icon-box box-pink mb-3"><i class="bi bi-book-half"></i></div>
              <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-2">Constitutional Grounding</h5>
              <p class="text-secondary-color fs-sm m-0">Every module integrates equality, justice, and fundamental rights.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Pillar 3 -->
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="feature-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4">
              <div class="feature-icon-box box-orange mb-3"><i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i></div>
              <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-2">Train the Trainer</h5>
              <p class="text-secondary-color fs-sm m-0">We create more trainers and leaders, not dependency on external forces.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Pillar 4 -->
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="feature-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4">
              <div class="feature-icon-box box-teal mb-3"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i></div>
              <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-2">Evidence-Based</h5>
              <p class="text-secondary-color fs-sm m-0">Behavioral change is tracked, measured, and made visible in real-time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 4. ORIGIN STORY -->
<section id="origin" class="py-5 bg-primary-custom position-relative">
  <!-- subtle background pattern -->
  <div class="pattern-dots pattern-dots-muted position-absolute w-100 h-100 top-0 left-0"></div>
  <div class="container py-5 reveal position-relative z-1">
    <div class="section-header text-center mb-5 pb-3">
      <h6 class="text-uppercase text-secondary-color fw-bold mb-3 text-tracking-2">Origin Story</h6>
      <h2 class="fw-bold section-title">Named After a <span class="gradient-text-2">Mother’s Resilience</span></h2>
      <p class="text-secondary-color mx-auto maxw-700">The origin of BeYa is rooted in lived experience, not theory.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0 order-2 order-lg-1">
        <div class="timeline-container ps-4">
          <div class="timeline-item mb-4 position-relative">
            <div class="timeline-dot gradient-bg-1"></div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color">The Realization: Motivation Fades</h5>
            <p class="text-secondary-color">Over 13 years and 300+ sessions reaching 100,000+ individuals, inspiration created intent, but weeks later people returned to old habits. The impact did not sustain.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item mb-4 position-relative">
            <div class="timeline-dot gradient-bg-2"></div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color">The Central Question</h5>
            <p class="text-secondary-color">How can behavioral training become a system of daily practice instead of a one-time emotional experience?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item mb-4 position-relative">
            <div class="timeline-dot gradient-bg-3"></div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color">The Turning Point</h5>
            <p class="text-secondary-color">A student asked: “We are not allowed to draw water from the public well because of our caste. How will learning these skills change that?” This revealed that skills alone only help people cope—understanding rights empowers them to refuse injustice.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item position-relative">
            <div class="timeline-dot gradient-bg-1"></div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color">The Outcome: System Built</h5>
            <p class="text-secondary-color">BeYa became a unified system integrating daily practice and constitutional awareness, named after a mother whose hospital experience proved that systems fail from a lack of structure, not intent.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 order-1 order-lg-2 mb-5">
        <div class="story-card p-4 p-md-5 rounded-4 border-glow shadow-glow-accent">
          <div class="origin-part origin-part-1 mb-4 pb-4 border-bottom border-secondary-custom">
            <span class="origin-step-label text-danger">01 &mdash; Background</span>
            <p class="text-primary-color fs-5 text-lh-18 mb-0">
              Sabith Ali grew up as the youngest of eight in rural Kerala. He lost his father early and funded his education through work.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="origin-part origin-part-2 mb-4 pb-4 border-bottom border-secondary-custom">
            <span class="origin-step-label" style="color: var(--color-pink);">02 &mdash; The Moment</span>
            <p class="text-primary-color fs-5 text-lh-18 mb-0">
              He watched his mother, living with paralysis, wait for hours in a hospital corridor without support, clarity, or dignity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="origin-part origin-part-pivot mb-4">
            <p class="origin-pivot-text mb-1">That experience changed everything.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="origin-part origin-part-4">
            <span class="origin-step-label" style="color: var(--color-teal);">04 &mdash; The Answer</span>
            <p class="text-primary-color fs-5 text-lh-18 mb-0">
              Every solution he built came from that moment. BeYa exists to ensure dignity is not given but built through structured, daily actions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 5. BEYA LIFE SKILLS PROGRAM -->
<section id="life-skills" class="py-5 section-darker border-top border-bottom border-secondary-custom">
  <div class="container py-5 reveal">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
      <h6 class="text-uppercase text-secondary-color fw-bold mb-4 text-tracking-2">Programs</h6>
      <div class="feature-icon-box feature-icon-box-lg box-blue mx-auto mb-3"><i class="bi bi-puzzle-fill fs-3"></i></div>
      <h2 class="fw-bold section-title"><span class="gradient-text-1">BeYa Trainings</span></h2>
      <p class="text-secondary-color mx-auto fs-5 maxw-800 mb-2">
        A daily practice-based life skills system designed to transform lives across families, schools, and workplaces. Built on the World Health Organization life skills framework and grounded in constitutional values such as fundamental rights, duties, and values.
      </p>
      <p class="fw-semibold text-primary-color fs-5 mt-3">One system. Three environments. Same transformation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 mt-2">
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="portal-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4">
          <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-3">Family Program</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary-color fs-sm mb-4">Parents and students practice together—building discipline, communication, and accountability through daily habits.</p>
          <ul class="portal-list pb-2 text-start mb-0 text-secondary-color border-bottom border-light-custom">
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-blue"></i> Joint commitment sessions</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-blue"></i> Daily reflections and conversations</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-blue"></i> Progress tracking through web app</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="portal-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4">
          <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-3">Schools Program</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary-color fs-sm mb-4">Integrates life skills and constitutional values into student life—not as lessons, but as daily practice.</p>
          <ul class="portal-list pb-2 text-start mb-0 text-secondary-color border-bottom border-light-custom">
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-pink"></i> Emotional regulation</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-pink"></i> Civic responsibility</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-pink"></i> Guided communication</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="portal-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4">
          <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-3">Corporate Program</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary-color fs-sm mb-4">Helps employees develop life skills that strengthen professional performance, improve work-life balance, and create harmony in their family life.</p>
          <ul class="portal-list pb-2 text-start mb-0 text-secondary-color border-bottom border-light-custom">
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-teal"></i> Emotional intelligence in the workplace</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-teal"></i> Leadership and conflict resolution</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-teal"></i> Work-life balance and stress management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-12 mt-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-4 border-glow shadow-sm bg-primary-custom d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center justify-content-between">
          <div class="mb-3 mb-md-0">
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-1">Core Add-ons</h5>
            <p class="text-secondary-color fs-sm mb-0">Every program strictly incorporates these powerful foundational pillars.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
            <span class="badge border border-glow text-accent bg-transparent px-3 py-2 fs-6">Train the Trainers</span>
            <span class="badge border border-glow text-blue bg-transparent px-3 py-2 fs-6">Constitutional Consciousness</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 6. MEDIBUK PROGRAM -->
<section id="medibuk" class="py-5 position-relative">
  <div class="container py-5 reveal">
    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-5 mb-5 mb-lg-0 pe-lg-4">
        <div class="feature-icon-box feature-icon-box-lg box-teal mx-auto mx-lg-0 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-heart-pulse-fill fs-3"></i></div>
        <h2 class="fw-bold section-title text-center text-lg-start"><span class="gradient-text-3">BeYa MediBuk</span></h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-color fs-5 text-center text-lg-start maxw-500">
          Born from a real hospital experience, BeYa MediBuk addresses a simple but critical problem — long waiting times and lack of dignity in patient care.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary-color fs-5 text-center text-lg-start maxw-500">
          BeYa MediBuk transforms outpatient systems by reducing waiting time, improving coordination, and restoring dignity to every patient experience.
        </p>
        <p class="fw-semibold text-primary-color text-center text-lg-start fs-5 mt-3">Two approaches. One goal — efficient systems with dignity at the center.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-7 ps-lg-5">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-4 border-glow shadow-glow-primary bg-card-custom mb-4 transition">
          <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-3">External Management Model</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary-color m-0">Trained BeYa teams are deployed within hospitals to directly manage patient flow, reduce waiting time, and improve coordination — ensuring immediate and visible impact.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-4 border-glow shadow-glow-primary bg-card-custom transition">
          <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary-color mb-3">Internal Training Model</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary-color m-0">Receptionists and OPD staff are trained to manage patient flow, communication, and coordination effectively — creating a strong internal system within the hospital. This approach enables easy scaling and long-term implementation without dependence on external teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

